  "comments": "The statues are unlabeled.  Mary and Jesus are obvious.  I'm guessing that the 4 statues to the left of the Holy Child over the entrance are based on the lineage in Matthew's Gospel and are David, Solomon, Joseph and Mary, and that the 4 to the right are Matthew, Mark, Luke and John.  I have no idea who the additional women around Mary and Jesus are at the top.  ",
